title: Lowest rural land area below 5 meters
description: In 2015, only 0.0029% of Jordan's rural land area was below 5 meters in elevation, one of the lowest percentages globally.

title: Lowest land area below 5 meters
description: In 2015, just 0.0043% of Jordan's total land area was below 5 meters in elevation, making it one of the lowest in the world.

title: Fastest time to obtain an electrical connection
description: In 2019, it took only 3.8 days to obtain an electrical connection in Jordan, one of the fastest times globally.

title: Lowest percentage of children in employment
description: In 2016, only 1.23% of children aged 7-14 were in employment in Jordan, one of the lowest rates worldwide.

title: Highest unemployment with advanced education, male
description: In 2023, 20.65% of Jordan's male labor force with advanced education was unemployed, one of the highest rates globally.
